\s1 Paul’s job  
\p
\v 14-15 My Christian friends, I’m sure that you already know about the things that I wrote in this letter. Before I started to write this letter, I remembered that you are good people and that you know a lot, and you even teach each other about the things I wrote about. But I got brave and started to write to you anyway, to get you to think a bit more about some of those things. God is good to me,  
\v 16 \w and|strong="G2316"\w* \w he|strong="G3588"\w* picked \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w out|strong="G1096"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w be|strong="G1096"\w* \w a|strong="G1096"\w* worker \w for|strong="G1519"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*. \w My|strong="G1722"\w* job \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* tell \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w good|strong="G3588"\w* \w news|strong="G2098"\w* \w about|strong="G1722"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w people|strong="G1484"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* \w not|strong="G1510"\w* Jews. \w After|strong="G1722"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* tell \w them|strong="G3588"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w good|strong="G3588"\w* \w news|strong="G2098"\w*, \w God|strong="G2316"\w*’s \w spirit|strong="G4151"\w* works \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w make|strong="G1519"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w* \w good|strong="G3588"\w* \w and|strong="G2316"\w* \w right|strong="G1519"\w*, \w and|strong="G2316"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* really happy \w with|strong="G1722"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w*. \w It|strong="G1510"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w like|strong="G2443"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w give|strong="G1096"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*, \w like|strong="G2443"\w* \w a|strong="G1096"\w* really \w good|strong="G3588"\w* gift.   
\p
\v 17 \w So|strong="G3767"\w* \w I|strong="G3767"\w* \w like|strong="G4314"\w* \w to|strong="G4314"\w* tell everybody \w about|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w things|strong="G3588"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w has|strong="G2192"\w* helped \w me|strong="G2192"\w* \w do|strong="G2192"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w my|strong="G1722"\w* work \w for|strong="G4314"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*.  
\v 18-19 But I will not talk about anything else. I just want to talk about whatever Jesus Christ did. He used me, but he is the one that did it. He got me to tell his true message to people that don’t know God, and his Holy Spirit got me to do powerful things too. After they heard my message and saw the things I did, they turned around and believed God. I started to tell people in Jerusalem the good message about Jesus Christ, and I kept on telling people that message everywhere I went, right out to Illyricum.  
\v 20 \w I|strong="G1161"\w* always want \w to|strong="G2443"\w* tell \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w good|strong="G2097"\w* story \w to|strong="G2443"\w* \w people|strong="G3361"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w have|strong="G5547"\w* \w never|strong="G3756"\w* heard \w about|strong="G1909"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G3756"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*. \w I|strong="G1161"\w* don’t want \w to|strong="G2443"\w* go \w to|strong="G2443"\w* places \w where|strong="G3699"\w* somebody \w else|strong="G3361"\w* already told \w them|strong="G2443"\w* \w about|strong="G1909"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G3756"\w*, \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w just|strong="G3779"\w* tell \w them|strong="G2443"\w* \w a|strong="G1909"\w* bit \w more|strong="G1161"\w*. \w No|strong="G3756"\w*, \w I|strong="G1161"\w* want \w to|strong="G2443"\w* go \w and|strong="G1161"\w* tell \w people|strong="G3361"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w* haven’t heard \w about|strong="G1909"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G3756"\w*.  
