\s1 Be careful, some people will tell you the wrong story  
\p
\v 17 Listen, \w my|strong="G4160"\w* Christian \w friends|strong="G3844"\w*, \w I|strong="G3739"\w*’m telling \w you|strong="G5210"\w* straight, \w you|strong="G5210"\w*’ve got \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w be|strong="G2532"\w* really careful \w about|strong="G4160"\w* \w people|strong="G4160"\w* \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w make|strong="G4160"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* split \w up|strong="G2532"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* argue \w with|strong="G3844"\w* each \w other|strong="G1161"\w*. \w Remember|strong="G4160"\w* \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* heard \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w true|strong="G3588"\w* message \w about|strong="G4160"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2532"\w* Christ, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w learned|strong="G3129"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w follow|strong="G1161"\w* \w his|strong="G4160"\w* \w way|strong="G3739"\w*, \w but|strong="G1161"\w* \w there|strong="G2532"\w* \w are|strong="G3588"\w* \w some|strong="G3739"\w* \w people|strong="G4160"\w* \w that|strong="G3739"\w* want \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* leave \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w way|strong="G3739"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w go|strong="G3739"\w* \w another|strong="G3739"\w* \w way|strong="G3739"\w*. \w They|strong="G2532"\w* tell \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* different story, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w get|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* argue \w with|strong="G3844"\w* each \w other|strong="G1161"\w*. \w So|strong="G2532"\w* don’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* listen \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w*. \w Keep|strong="G4160"\w* \w away|strong="G1578"\w* \w from|strong="G3844"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w*.  
\v 18 \w They|strong="G2532"\w* don’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* work \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w our|strong="G2532"\w* leader, \w Jesus|strong="G2532"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*, \w but|strong="G2532"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w just|strong="G2532"\w* work \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w themselves|strong="G1438"\w*. \w They|strong="G2532"\w* try \w to|strong="G2532"\w* trick \w people|strong="G3588"\w*. \w They|strong="G2532"\w* talk really nicely \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w people|strong="G3588"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w say|strong="G1223"\w* \w good|strong="G1223"\w* \w things|strong="G3588"\w* \w about|strong="G3588"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w*. \w They|strong="G2532"\w* \w do|strong="G2532"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w get|strong="G2532"\w* whatever \w they|strong="G2532"\w* want \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w themselves|strong="G1438"\w*. \w They|strong="G2532"\w* trick \w people|strong="G3588"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* don’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* think \w about|strong="G3588"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* properly.  
\v 19 \w But|strong="G1161"\w* don’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* \w let|strong="G1161"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w* trick \w you|strong="G5210"\w*. \w Everyone|strong="G3956"\w* knows \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w do|strong="G1510"\w* \w what|strong="G3588"\w* \w God|strong="G1519"\w* \w wants|strong="G2309"\w*, \w so|strong="G3767"\w* \w I|strong="G1161"\w*’m happy \w about|strong="G1909"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*. \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w I|strong="G1161"\w* \w also|strong="G1161"\w* \w want|strong="G2309"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* tell \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w be|strong="G1510"\w* careful. \w I|strong="G1161"\w* \w want|strong="G2309"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* understand \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w things|strong="G3956"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* \w good|strong="G3956"\w*, \w and|strong="G1161"\w* don’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* \w even|strong="G1161"\w* think \w about|strong="G1909"\w* doing \w the|strong="G1519"\w* \w things|strong="G3956"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* \w bad|strong="G2556"\w*.  
\v 20 \w You|strong="G5210"\w* \w know|strong="G1722"\w*, \w Satan|strong="G4567"\w*, \w the|strong="G1722"\w* boss \w over|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* bad spirits, \w he|strong="G1161"\w* tries \w to|strong="G1722"\w* get \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w to|strong="G1722"\w* go wrong. \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* stronger than \w Satan|strong="G4567"\w*. \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w one|strong="G3588"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* makes \w us|strong="G2249"\w* happy \w and|strong="G1161"\w* quiet \w inside|strong="G1722"\w* \w ourselves|strong="G2249"\w*. \w And|strong="G1161"\w* \w he|strong="G1161"\w* \w will|strong="G2316"\w* beat \w Satan|strong="G4567"\w*, \w so|strong="G1161"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w Satan|strong="G4567"\w* can’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* \w do|strong="G1722"\w* anything \w to|strong="G1722"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w any|strong="G1722"\w* \w more|strong="G1161"\w*.  
\p \w I|strong="G1473"\w* ask \w our|strong="G2316"\w* leader, \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w*, \w to|strong="G1722"\w* \w be|strong="G2316"\w* really \w good|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G1722"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*.   
\b  
\iex (The next part, 16:21-24, says things for just some of the people at Rome at that time, so we have not translated it yet.)  
\s1 Everybody has to tell God that he is good  
\p
\v 25-27 God is really great and powerful, so everybody has to tell him that he is good. He can make you strong. This is his message. It is the good news about Jesus Christ. A long time ago, God planned to get both the Jewish people, and the people that are not Jews, to believe in him. But at first he kept it a secret, and he just got the Jewish people to follow him. After that, he got his men to write about it ahead of time, and their words are in his book. Now his message about Jesus is for every nation. It is not just for the Jewish people, but everybody everywhere can trust him, and they can listen to him and do what he wants. God is the only one that can think good enough to make it all work out like that. So everybody has to tell God and Jesus Christ, “You are great.” They have always got to do that for ever.  
\b  
\p \sig From Paul\sig*   